data.title: The First Slave Ship in Curaçao - Curaçao History
data.meta_description: CuracaoHistory.com strives to have a positive impact on the life of our citizens by making our island's history easily and freely accessible to anyone who has a computer or smartphone and an internet connection.
data.text:
CuraçaoHistory.com strives to have a positive impact on the life of our citizens.

Citizens who are well aware of our island's history will be proud of our culture and will share our culture with visitors, creating a ripple effect in our tourism.
